data.description: This charming 2 bedroom 1 bathroom home boasts a cozy 660 square feet of living space and sits gracefully on a spacious corner lot with a BRAND NEW ROOF! As you approach, you'll be welcomed by the serene ambiance created by the lush, shady trees that envelop the property. The big front yard, enclosed by a sturdy fence, provides a secure and private oasis for outdoor activities and relaxation. Inside, the well-designed layout maximizes every inch of living space, making this home both practical and inviting. Whether you are looking for a peaceful retreat or a cozy starter home, this property offers a delightful blend of comfort and outdoor beauty.
